snippet.title: Paralegal Reacts To Amber Heard Doctored TMZ Video! FULL VIDEO SHOWS HER LAUGHING
snippet.description:
PARALEGAL REACTS TO JOHNNY DEPP V. AMBER HEARD

So today I reacted to the FULL video of the "Explosive Fight" that was sold to TMZ by Amber Heard. I know TMZ owns the rights to this video because as soon as I uploaded it, it was copyright claimed BY TMZ. This means TMZ owns the rights to the video and I believe it was sold to them by Amber Heard. That’s the logical deduction! All ad money goes to them, but it doesn't matter, getting the word out does! But it turns out Amber Heard or TMZ edited/doctored the footage. I am including the full unedited version in this video.

SOURCE: Nick Wallis website, link here - https://www.nickwallis.com/depp-trial-evidence

Also gonna link Lost Beyond Pluto, who is a lawyer who breaks down the legality of this case very professionally: https://www.youtube.com/c/lostbeyondpluto

Link to Incredibly Average, he has covered this case in depth from beginning to very recently.. including animated re-enactments etc. Highly recommend!: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCg0C-N_MPYYOXyF4T3jMxNQ

Thank you so much for the love on my last videos I really appreciate it! It's really motivating me to keep it up. I hope this was helpful or enjoyable in some way. I plan to keep up with this case so stay tuned and make sure you are subscribed and turn your notification bell on!

Email: Debidooms@gmail.com
Instagram: debidoesmakeup
TikTok: debidooms

DISCLAIMER:: This video is all my OPINION based on my professional capacity as a Paralegal and on the public information on this case. Please do not take anything I say as fact and come to your own conclusions based on the evidence presented. Everything stated is alleged and my own opinion which is a direct result of my research on this case, however I do not have access to any information that is not public.
